original: <color=#FFE787>回復時間：</color><color=#ccffcc>$Skill_CD(3251)@</color>短時間內發出七下刺擊，以<color=#ccffcc>$Skill_Str(3251)@</color><color=#80cc00>武力</color>對敵人造成物理傷害。
text: <color=#FFE787>Response time: </color><color=#ccffcc>$Skill_CD(3251)@</color> sends out seven stabbings in a short period of time, with <color=#ccffcc>$Skill_Str( 3251)@</color><color=#80cc00>War</color> causes physical damage to the enemy.
